          "name": "Icon of Obstinacy",
          "type": "Abilities",
          "lines": [
            {
              "name": "Description",
              "value": "While this model is leading a unit, each time an attack targets that unit, if the Strength characteristic of that attack is greater than or equal to the Toughness characteristic of that unit, subtract 1 from the Wound roll."
