          "name": "Oath of Rynn",
          "type": "Abilities",
          "lines": [
            {
              "name": "Description",
              "value": "Once per battle, at the start of either player’s Command phase, this model can use this ability. When it does, until the end of the turn, add 1 to the Attacks characteristic of weapons equipped by models in this model’s unit."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "To the Last",
          "type": "Abilities",
          "lines": [
            {
              "name": "Description",
              "value": "While this model is leading a unit, each time a model in that unit makes an attack, add 1 to the Hit roll if that unit is below its Starting Strength, and add 1 to the Wound roll as well if that unit is Below Half-strength."
            }
          ]
        },
